#CREATE TWO VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS , INSTALL FEW PACKAGES IN THE FIRST ONE . HOW DO YOU CRATE A SIMILAR ENVIRONMENT IN THE SECOND ONE?

🎯 Step 1: Create the First Virtual Environment
    python -m venv env1

🔁 Step 2: Activate env1
    env1\Scripts\activate

📦 Step 3: Install Some Packages in env1
    pip install numpy pandas flask

📝 Step 4: Freeze Requirements of env1
    pip freeze > requirements.txt

🆕 Step 5: Create the Second Virtual Environment
    python -m venv env2

🔁 Step 6: Activate env2
    env2\Scripts\activate

📥 Step 7: Install Same Packages in env2
    pip install -r requirements.txt
